<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="offer-n">offer <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'ɒfə(r)/    美 /'ɔːfər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>提供 (物)；提议：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>accept / refuse an offer</strong>
提供 (物)；提议：</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>made an offer</strong> of help.
他主动提供帮助。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you got any <strong>job offers</strong>?
有公司愿意聘用你吗？</p><footer>2008 辽宁</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>开价；报价：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He asked the crowd in the auction-room to <strong>make offers</strong>, or “bids” for the items on sale.
他让拍卖厅里的人开价或竞拍在售物品。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>减价；特价：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>free offers</strong> / a <strong>special offer</strong> 
免费赠品/特价优惠</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-offer">on offer</h3>
<p>1.<strong>削价 / 特价出售的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This computer was on special offer.
这款电脑正特价出售。</p><footer>2010 浙江改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Come down to our restaurant to enjoy the special dishes on offer.
来我们餐馆享受提供的特价菜吧。</p><footer>2008 江西改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Can I help you with it?
— I appreciate your <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (好意), but I can manage it myself.  （2012 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. offer  </p></div>